Happy Labor Day Daniel!

The world changes when someone refuses to accept the status quo. That someone is you.

When no one else is keeping score, you keep going.

You persist through late nights and setbacks because you believe in your idea.

Your creativity and effort deserve to be celebrated, and not only today. This is how progress happens!

Thank you for laboring to create a better future for all of us.

Take a moment to reflect: Whats a win youve had recently, big or small?

Wed love to hear it. Share it with us by replying to this email.

Were grateful youre part of our community.

Stephen Key, Andrew Krauss, and the inventRight Team
